Package com.mirasense.scanditsdk.interfaces

Interface Summary
ScanditSDK Controls the barcode scanning process and camera access of the Scandit SDK.
ScanditSDKListener Interface defining callback methods invoked by Scandit SDK scan view to update application.
ScanditSDKOverlay Interface of all the possible customization options for the standard GUI which is displayed on top of the video feed running the recognition.
